7_4	0.17253377	The rules, almost a decade in the making, would bar the use of genetically engineered crops, disease-killing irradiation treatments or industrial sludge as a fertilizer.
7_5	0.22718743	Products grown and processed according to the standards and contain at least 95 percent organic ingredients will be allowed to carry a seal of approval that says, ''USDA Certified Organic''.
7_6	0.25872934	Foods that are least 50 percent organic could be labeled ''made with'' organic ingredients.
